<ul>
    <li>Proper tax invoices with company registration details</li>
    <li>Payment terms (typically net 30 days)</li>
    <li>Multiple authorization signatures</li>
    <li>Separate billing for accommodation vs. services</li>
    <li>Monthly statements for accounting reconciliation</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Extended Stay Service Expectations</h3>
